{"id":17044,"date":"2019-04-24T00:30:38","date_gmt":"2019-04-23T17:30:38","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=17044"},"modified":"2019-06-27T15:07:22","modified_gmt":"2019-06-27T08:07:22","slug":"dung-trello-de-viet-bai-bang-smartphone","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/usecase\/dung-trello-de-viet-bai-bang-smartphone","title":{"rendered":"Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng Trello \u0111\u1ec3 VI\u1ebeT B\u00c0I tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i di \u0111\u1ed9ng"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 <strong>vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i<\/strong> th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft blog \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0o k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n \u0111ang \u0111i du l\u1ecbch v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>H\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec7n nay \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng minh, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i th\u00ec n\u00f3 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n r\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p blogging c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng <strong><a href=\"\/out\/trello\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Trello (opens in a new tab)\">Trello<\/a> <\/strong>&#8211; \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay &#8211; \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng chuy\u00ean vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Evernote, iWriter, Note,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Trello s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o Final Draft cho b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua vi\u1ec7c l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch, nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u00e0 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1eddi gian r\u00e3nh r\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u1ecdi l\u00fac m\u1ecdi n\u01a1i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Markdown &#8211; Chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u0103n b\u1ea3n sang HTML nhanh ch\u00f3ng ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"764\" height=\"562\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Markdown-Trello.png\" alt=\"Markdown Trello\" class=\"wp-image-17073\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Markdown-Trello.png 764w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Markdown-Trello-218x160.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Markdown-Trello-300x221.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Markdown-Trello-700x515.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 764px) 100vw, 764px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Trello h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 <strong>Markdown <\/strong>gi\u00fap \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ho\u00e1 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh vi\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1eeba vi\u1ebft v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u00fac, ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Markdown l\u00e0 g\u00ec? <strong>Markdown <\/strong>l\u00e0 ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u v\u0103n b\u1ea3n nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i v\u0103n b\u1ea3n th\u00e0nh HTML nhanh nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m si\u00eau c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a <strong>Markdown <\/strong>l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00ec d\u1ec5 nh\u1edb, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nhanh thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c. V\u00ec v\u1eady Markdown ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n nh\u1edb m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n sau l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Heading 1: #<\/li><li>Heading 2: ##<\/li><li>Heading 3: ###<\/li><li>List bullet: *<\/li><li>B\u00f4i \u0111en: **v\u0103n b\u1ea3n**<\/li><li>Ch\u1eef nghi\u00eang: *v\u0103n b\u1ea3n*<\/li><li>Link: [achor text](https:\/\/rootdomain.com)<\/li><li>List s\u1ed1: 1. 2. 3.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1edb xong, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i theo c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb: T\u1ea1o b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ebb Trello c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"640\" height=\"416\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Trello-New-Board.jpg\" alt=\"Trello New Board\" class=\"wp-image-17074\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Trello-New-Board.jpg 640w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Trello-New-Board-218x142.jpg 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Trello-New-Board-300x195.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><figcaption>T\u1ea1o b\u1ea3ng Trello m\u1edbi<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Trello b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Trello. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Trello mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1ea3i \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Trello v\u00e0 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"iOS  (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/us\/app\/trello-organize-anything\/id461504587?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">iOS <\/a>hay <a href=\"https:\/\/play.google.com\/store\/apps\/details?id=com.trello&amp;hl=vi\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Android (opens in a new tab)\">Android<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o b\u1ea3ng (Trello Board). B\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n sau n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ecdi b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 IDEA POOL (b\u1ea3ng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. T\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng Trello Power-Up \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m th\u00f4ng tin keyword cho m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon-1024x533.png\" alt=\"Power Ups Addon\" class=\"wp-image-17076\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon-1024x533.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon-218x113.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon-300x156.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon-700x364.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon-768x400.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Power-Ups-addon.png 1921w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Trello cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 Power-Ups MI\u1ec4N PH\u00cd m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Trello \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Trello cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t M\u1ed8T Trello Addon mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed cho m\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t addon c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng cho b\u1ea1n b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n b\u1ea3ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n (B\u1ea3ng team th\u00ec gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n \u1edf 10 b\u1ea3ng). M\u1ed7i b\u1ea3ng kh\u00e1c nhau b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t Addon kh\u00e1c nhau ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho t\u1eebng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u1edf b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t Addon custom field. Addon n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o field t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m th\u00f4ng tin keyword c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 keyword \u0111i k\u00e8m, h\u00e3y \u0111i\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i keyword v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 keyword, volume, KD,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. T\u1ea1o outline \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fac b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng Markdown \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o d\u00e0n b\u00e0i c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1o TH\u1eba B\u00c0I VI\u1ebeT CH\u00cdNH (Trello Card) v\u1edbi outline (minh h\u1ecda) nh\u01b0 sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1: #Ti\u00eau \u0110\u1ec1<\/li><li>\u00dd th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t: ##Heading 2<ul><li>\u00dd ph\u1ee5 tr\u1ee3 th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t: ###heading 3<\/li><li>\u00dd ph\u1ee5 tr\u1ee3 th\u1ee9 hai: ###heading 3<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>\u00dd th\u1ee9 hai: ##Heading 3<\/li><li>\u00dd th\u1ee9 ba: ##Heading 3<br>&#8230;<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"759\" height=\"431\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Outline.png\" alt=\"Outline\" class=\"wp-image-17077\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Outline.png 759w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Outline-218x124.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Outline-300x170.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Outline-700x397.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 759px) 100vw, 759px\" \/><figcaption>Outline m\u1eabu minh h\u1ecda<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 h\u01a1n, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng <a href=\"https:\/\/trello.com\/b\/0ibgTOgj\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Trello m\u1eabu t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y (opens in a new tab)\">Trello m\u1eabu t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a> cho b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"highlight\"><em>Ch\u00fa \u00fd: B\u1ea1n b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft Markdown c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp \u1edf ph\u1ea7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 thu\u1ea7n th\u1ee5c vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean Trello. Markdown v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1eefu \u00edch v\u00ec ngo\u00e0i Trello b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng cho nhi\u1ec1u \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c n\u1eefa.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><strong>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh<\/strong>. B\u1ea1n copy tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o th\u1ebb Trello Card d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng qua thao t\u00e1c copy paste (clipboard copy).<\/li><li><strong>Trang web tham kh\u1ea3o<\/strong>. Trello c\u0169ng cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n th\u00eam link \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh file \u1ea3nh.<\/li><li><strong>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u kh\u00e1c<\/strong>. C\u00e1c file \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng pdf, word, excel,&#8230; \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m v\u00e0o th\u1ebb Trello.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u ri\u00eang. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n LI\u00caN K\u1ebeT HAI CHI\u1ec0U c\u00e1c th\u1ebb nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi th\u1ebb b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft ch\u00ednh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"769\" height=\"597\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/connect-2-cards.png\" alt=\"Connect 2 Cards\" class=\"wp-image-17078\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/connect-2-cards.png 769w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/connect-2-cards-218x169.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/connect-2-cards-300x233.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/connect-2-cards-700x543.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/connect-2-cards-768x596.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 769px) 100vw, 769px\" \/><figcaption>K\u1ebft n\u1ed1i 2 chi\u1ec1u 2 th\u1ebb v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 BACK v\u1ec1 th\u1ebb vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem B\u1ea3ng Trello m\u1eabu \u1edf ph\u1ea7n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>5. Copy v\u00e0o WordPress v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Trello \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh 80% b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh chu v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 copy v\u00e0o b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n qu\u00e9t ch\u1ecdn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 (kh\u00f4ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda) v\u00e0 copy. Xong paste v\u00e0o WordPress. Nh\u1edd Markdown n\u00ean v\u0103n b\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng thu\u1ea7n HTML. R\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"742\" height=\"420\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Copy-bai-viet.png\" alt=\"Copy Bai Viet\" class=\"wp-image-17079\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Copy-bai-viet.png 742w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Copy-bai-viet-218x123.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Copy-bai-viet-300x170.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Copy-bai-viet-700x396.png 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 742px) 100vw, 742px\" \/><figcaption>Copy b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch qu\u00e9t v\u00e0 copy &gt;&gt; Paste v\u00e0o WordPress<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o th\u00eam <strong>Feature Image<\/strong> v\u00e0 ch\u00e8n c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh (nh\u01b0 h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh screenshot). V\u00e0 c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>M\u1eb9o hay khi d\u00f9ng Trello vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>B\u1ea1n xu\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng (Enter x2) 2 l\u1ea7n cho m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng Markdown \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng v\u0103n b\u1ea3n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb l\u1ed7i.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n b\u00eca c\u1ee7a th\u1ebb b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ch\u00e8n \u1ea3nh v\u00e0o th\u1ebb \u0111\u00f3.<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n \u1ea3nh th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u0103n b\u1ea3n Trello v\u1edbi Markdown khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e8n \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 URL ngo\u00e0i WordPress nh\u01b0 Google Photos. <pre>![anh]https:\/\/url-cua-anh.jpg)<\/pre><\/li><li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng comment \u1edf th\u1ebb v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u01b0u \u00fd hay tr\u00edch d\u1eabn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n thay v\u00ec \u0111\u00ednh k\u00e8m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o th\u1ebb.<\/li><li>Trello h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 emoji r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t ???? v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n v\u00e0o b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u bao g\u1ed3m Ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1ebb.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u00f4i d\u00f9ng Trello \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i tr\u00ean di d\u1ed9ng thay cho <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"\/out\/evernote\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Evernote<\/strong><\/a> v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Evernote hay \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng kh\u00e1c, Trello cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn to\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh thay v\u00ec c\u1ee5c b\u1ed9.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n vi\u1ebft tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean th\u1ebb Trello s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng v\u00ec Markdown \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean Trello ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh g\u1ea7n 80% b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ec9nh s\u1eeda m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u1ea3nh b\u00eca cho b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng m\u00e1y t\u00ednh. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>C\u00f2n b\u1ea1n th\u00ec sao? B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng th\u1eed d\u00f9ng Trello \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i ch\u01b0a? H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u1edf d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e9<\/em>!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i tr\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 th\u00ec h\u00e3y suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i b\u1edfi v\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111ang d\u00f9ng \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng TRELLO \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft b\u00e0i blog c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":17083,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"close","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[198],"tags":[57,73,77],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello.png",1150,575,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello-700x350.png",700,350,true],"medium_large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello-768x384.png",768,384,true],"large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello-1024x512.png",1024,512,true],"1536x1536":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello.png",1150,575,false],"2048x2048":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello.png",1150,575,false],"pk-small":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello.png",80,40,false],"pk-thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Viet-bai-voi-trello.png",300,150,false]},"post_excerpt_stackable":"<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n ngh\u0129 vi\u1ebft b\u00e0i tr